---
title: Chicken & Halloumi DIY Pita with Fresh Dough, Chopped Salad & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Let’s try a fun new way to use pizza dough! How about we turn them into pita pockets, packed full of juicy chermoula chicken,
halloumi, and a zingy chopped salad? Don’t forget to spread on some tangy garlic yoghurt for extra creaminess and flavour.
